HYPRE

This document is the home hypre web page and describes the goals
of the hypre program.

    http://www.llnl.gov/casc/hypre/

Legal stuff (copyright, disclaimer, licensing restrictions, etc.)
can be found in the file COPYRIGHT, and through the hypre software
distribution page

    http://www.llnl.gov/casc/hypre/download/hypre_agree.html

To install this package, please see chapter 8.1 in the "HYPRE
Users Manual".

The "HYPRE Users Manual" is available from:

    http://www.llnl.gov/casc/hypre/pubs/HYPRE_usr_manual.ps

The "HYPRE Reference Manual" can be found at:

    http://www.llnl.gov/casc/hypre/pubs/HYPRE_ref_manual.ps

An overview of the differences between releases of hypre can be found
in the file CHANGELOG

To subscribe to the mailing list "New Release Announcements (hypre-
announce)" or "New Beta Release Announcements (hypre-beta-announce) 
go to

    http://www.llnl.gov/CASC/hypre/maillists/get_subscription.cgi

We appreciate feedback from users of this package. Please submit
comments, suggestions, and bug reports to 

    http://www-casc.llnl.gov/bugs/enter_bug.cgi?product=HYPRE
